  "format": "Sean Fennessey and Amanda Dobbins are joined by Justin Charity to talk through Spike Lee's career and favorite films, then dig into 'Da 5 Bloods,' his Vietnam War heist movie about four Black veterans returning for buried gold and their squad leader's remains.",
